CREATING TITLE AND LOGO 10

Before we start creating title we need to fix the page formatting by following step below

STEP 1- Click on the page, go to formatting, change the background to #66666 and 66% transparency

STEP 2 -Page size, click type dropdown and select custom, make the width =1500 pixel and height= 800 pixel 

Creating title

STEP 3 - Click on the home tab, select the text box.

STEP 4 – General X position = 10, y position = 0, width = 920, height = 110 

STEP 5- Turn on the background, make the color custom #bda6c6  and 0%trnasparnsy

STEP 6- Click on inside text box and type GLOBAL SUPER STORE. Text size=44, Font=Arial Black, Font color=Custom 2e1039 and make it Bold

Follow the GIF below to apply the above steps 

Create Colaberry Logo

You can find the logo in the file you download in the first steps 

STEP 7- Click on the Insert tab, image, and browse for the image  in the folder you saved it in first step.

STEP 8 Go to General X position = 772, y position = 0, width = 160, height = 110

Follow the GIF below to apply the above steps
